"{\"uid\": \"cityam.com-copper-box-to-host-gb-basketball-fixtures-ahead-of-paris-2024-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 45, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 47, \"to\": 92, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 94, \"to\": 139, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By:Matt Hardy  Deputy Sports Editor - City AM  Great Britain will host a pair of basketball internationals in July as the sport prepares for theParis 2024Olympics in the summer.\", \"from\": 141, \"to\": 318, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 188, \"end\": 201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9805650286302949, \"rank\": 0.019802677888423575, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_national_field_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The GB Basketball men's team will take on South Sudan on Thursday 18 July at the Copper Box while the women will take on Germany on Sunday 21 July.\", \"from\": 320, \"to\": 467, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics will see both five versus five and three versus three competitions this summer with South Sudan qualified for the men's 5\\u00d75 and Germany qualified for the women's 5\\u00d75 and 3\\u00d73.\", \"from\": 469, \"to\": 656, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Great Britain has not qualified for any basketball discipline at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 658, \"to\": 736, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 658, \"end\": 671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9805650286302949, \"rank\": 0.019802677888423575, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_national_field_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It comes as USA basketball stars such as LeBron James will face South Sudan and Germany at the O2 Arena.\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 842, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 750, \"end\": 764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Basketball\", \"score\": 0.9998417514596147, \"rank\": 0.0001582735869972087, \"text\": \"USA basketball\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Basketball\"}, {\"begin\": 779, \"end\": 791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LeBron James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}, {\"begin\": 802, \"end\": 813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Sudan\", \"score\": 0.9948914852890448, \"rank\": 0.005134568149233123, \"text\": \"South Sudan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Sudan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Sudan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stay in the game with The Turnover: your weekly roundup of sport business news, expert analysis and behind\\u2011the\\u2011scenes stories from City\\u202fAM's sports desk.\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 997, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"These games are taking place just ahead of the Paris 2024 Olympics but we already have our sights set on the journey to the Los Angeles Games in 2028,\\\" GB Basketball chair, Chris Grant, said.\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1191, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1124, \"end\": 1135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999587776971691, \"rank\": 1.9409521090667523e-05, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 1173, \"end\": 1184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Grant_(footballer)\", \"score\": 0.9203145476428165, \"rank\": 0.08658008658009071, \"text\": \"Chris Grant\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13414980\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Grant_(footballer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Grant_(footballer)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is no doubt that we have the talent to be a force both on and off the court.\", \"from\": 1192, \"to\": 1275, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The momentum is building, and we would love to see as many fans of British Basketball as possible filling the seats at the Copper Box to support the players as we take our next steps.\\\"\", \"from\": 1277, \"to\": 1462, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1345, \"end\": 1352, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9991902554363985, \"rank\": 0.0005259166610225521, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is an exciting new era for GB Basketball following our work to rebuild and raise standards in recent months.\\\"\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1579, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Share this article  Subscribe to the City AM newsletter to have our top stories delivered directly to your inbox.\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1694, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow us for breaking news and latest updates\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1742, \"entities\": []}]}"